{"word":"G1254 - διακωλύω - diakōlýō - dee-ak-o-loo'-o - Forbid","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διακωλύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diakōlýō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-ak-o-loo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Forbid</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தடைசெய்"},{"paragraph":"to hinder, prevent"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G2967 - κωλύω - kōlýō - ko-loo'-o/2967\">G2967</a>; to <i>hinder altogether</i>, that is, <i>utterly prohibit:</i> - forbid.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}